{
  "stem": "14613.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody would try to steal whatever they could-- bakery, food, all the places.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And here is what I don't remember-- how did we get out from ghetto?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- this particular part is completely, what I believe they call tabula rasa-- my mind is blank.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To such an extent that, later on, my sister told me-- the last day in ghetto, which I still could not visualize-- and she said, when all these aussiedlung were taking place from ghetto, we hid ourselves in like a double wall.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a [NON-ENGLISH], or something there, like this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Germans came in, and somehow they found us and they chased us out to the-- to the trucks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from there, we went to [NON-ENGLISH], and we went to the freight cars.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is how we ended the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if she would not tell me, I would not know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there's no reason that she would tell me anything wrong, but this part of the aussiedlung is completely blank in my mind.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I imagine it is because of a, what happened on the fields, where we lost everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was number one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then number two, when we were found-- this is what she tells me-- when we were found by the Germans there, that was also-- had an impact on my mind or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That just blanked out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
